{"tid":307811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［非gay]一人一個扑野失敗既經驗","createTime":"2017-07-03T15:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T16:36:05.000Z","uid":101455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ae9e33bb157df87f1a0e1ee385e40dd5852134","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"話說今日去左女朋友屋企整電腦"},{"pid":"4da3ad30b5b342fbd872c4dfbba54f155d728bb3","tid":307811,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說今日去左女朋友屋企整電腦</blockquote><br />\n點知佢呀媽返咗嚟<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入作故仔"},{"pid":"acb2a65dfa52295293f809136e5702358bc56ff6","tid":307811,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話說今日去左女朋友屋企整電腦</blockquote><br />\n點知佢呀媽返咗嚟<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入作故仔</blockquote><br />\n伯母入左浴室沖涼放左對黑絲起廁所門口拎左黎係咁索"},{"pid":"32b29ce83c17c63fecb01edabc82b869486242fd","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"佢好淫 但佢屋企好嚴<br />\n伯母係屋企果時我地都坐定定搞電腦<br />\n我地等伯母出左去買餸先敢亂摷<br />\n摷到咁上下真係好想扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我緊係唔會開口講 <br />\n驚嚇親佢又話我猴擒<br />\n但我女朋友今次竟然主動開口話好想扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩！大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻硬到鐵咁<br />\n條淫娃仲走去偷伯母啲dom黎比我<br />\n身為青頭既我 終於要破處啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次用 感覺好奇妙 又滑又薄<br />\n唔知佢呀爸細定我粗 我戴到緊緊地<br />\n個心果時已經暗爽左<br />\n好啦 套就戴左 仲摸埋個閪窿係邊<br />\n果時個淫娃已經濕晒！<br />\n我地仲開埋電視個lift cctv<br />\n睇住伯母幾時番<br />\n當我準備插入去果時 <br />\n就見到佢呀媽個閪樣入緊lift<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n連個閪都未掂到我又要著番條褲<br />\n個套仲戴左個幾鐘先記得拎番出黎<br />\n屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc2846c021afef82fe2fff49c55e64312cecfce","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:02:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話說今日去左女朋友屋企整電腦</blockquote><br />\n點知佢呀媽返咗嚟<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入作故仔</blockquote><br />\n伯母入左浴室沖涼放左對黑絲起廁所門口拎左黎係咁索</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家唔好咁 我今日太緊張"},{"pid":"edad1c8339f987672b844e89a58e814fb348d4f2","tid":307811,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"冇房？  即刻入房屌啦"},{"pid":"7e1b23369c34ce7cddae37cb968c38a764a20c94","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇房？  即刻入房屌啦</blockquote><br />\n屌佢間房無鎖架！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0758d6851464a815f0e1bf05973b76eafc9435","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"無可能得我一個失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6cd7724f668677506d1f7270b2e60a4d20656e","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4f50f797f04349c7c81abd6eda4cc7923d6107","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84e931a52bff7ab61095bbb33005005d667082f","tid":307811,"uid":101455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:14:09.000Z","ms